query.esql:
from logs-corelight.various*
| where event.dataset == "notice" and (notice.note is not null or source.ip is not null  or destination.ip is not null or network.transport is not null or notice.p is not null)and notice.message is not null and severity.level is not null
| limit 10000
| stats values(severity.name),values(severity.level), count() by severity.name 
| eval severity_display = concat(`values(severity.name)`," (",to_string(`values(severity.level)`),")")
| rename severity_display as Severity, `count()` as Total
| keep Severity, Total

from logs-corelight.various*
| where event.dataset == "notice" and (notice.note is not null or source.ip is not null  or destination.ip is not null or network.transport is not null or notice.p is not null)and notice.message is not null and severity.level is not null
| limit 10000
| stats values(severity.name),values(severity.level), count() by severity.name 
| eval severity_display = concat(`values(severity.name)`," (",to_string(`values(severity.level)`),")")
| rename severity_display as Severity, `count()` as Total
| keep Severity, Total

from logs-corelight.various-*
| where event.dataset == "notice" and (notice.note is not null or source.ip is not null  or destination.ip is not null or network.transport is not null or notice.p is not null)and notice.message is not null and severity.level is not null
| limit 10000
| stats values(notice.note), values(network.transport), values(destination.port), values(severity.name),values(severity.level) by notice.note, severity.name, severity.level, destination.port
| eval severity_display = concat(`values(severity.name)`," (",to_string(`values(severity.level)`),")"), pp = concat(`values(network.transport)`,"/",to_string(`values(destination.port)`))
| stats values(pp), values(severity_display) by `values(notice.note)`, `values(severity.name)`
| rename `values(notice.note)` as Notes, `values(severity_display)` as Severity, `values(pp)` as Protocol
| keep Notes, Severity, Protocol
